high_descs: Turn around, go across the room and head to the small table in the corner.
Pick up the newspaper from the table.
Turn around, go half way across the room and turn left towards the small table with the laptop on it.
Put the newspaper on the end of the table.
Go across the room to the brown chair.
Pick up the newspaper from the brown chair.
Turn around, go across the room, turn left towards the small table with the laptop.
Put the newspaper between the laptop and the other newspaper on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put two newspapers on the small table.

high_descs: Turn around and move to stand at the end of the sofa closest to the small brown end table in the corner.
Pick up the newspaper from the end table.
Turn back around and carry the newspaper to the end of the coffee table, so the television is behind you.
Place the newspaper on the edge of the coffee table closest to you.
Move straight across the room to the chair in front of the window.
Pick up the newspaper from the chair.
Turn around and move back to the end of the coffee table where you put the other newspaper.
Place the newspaper on the table close to the computer.
anns.task_desc: Move two newspapers to the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the end table to the left of the couch.
Pick up the newspaper on the end table.
Turn right and take one step and turn right again, take six steps and turn left to face the coffee table.
Put the newspaper, standing vertically, in front of the gold hoop.
Walk straight forward to the end of the coffee table and turn right and then left to face the chair.
Pick up the newspaper from the chair.
Turn left for one step and then turn left again, walk forward to the TV and turn around.
Place the newspaper standing vertically, in front of the open laptop.
anns.task_desc: Place two newspapers, vertically, on the coffee table.
